data.name: textArea.Text
data.value: DSAS has detected that these data contain two shoreline proxies (MHW, HWL) and a proxy-datum bias correction has been applied. Shoreline forecasting will be referenced to MHW, however some transects only intersect shorelines referenced to HWL. DSAS can skip shoreline forecasting at transects where MHW data are unavailable, or can proceed with forecasting a shoreline position at every transect using the average proxy-datum bias data.
